flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> PreData["<b>Pre-training Data</b><br/>Billions of words<br/>Wikipedia, Books, Web<br/>Unlabeled Text"]

    PreData --> PreTrain["<b>Pre-training Phase</b><br/>Self-supervised Learning<br/>• BERT: Mask words, predict them<br/>• GPT: Predict next word<br/>• T5: Text-to-text tasks"]

    PreTrain --> PreModel["<b>Pre-trained Model</b><br/>General Language Understanding<br/>• Grammar<br/>• Facts<br/>• Reasoning patterns<br/>• Word relationships"]

    PreModel --> Save["💾 Save Model Weights<br/>θ_pretrain"]

    Save --> FTData["<b>Fine-tuning Data</b><br/>Thousands of examples<br/>Task-specific labels<br/>• Sentiment: (review, positive/negative)<br/>• NER: (text, entity tags)<br/>• QA: (question, context, answer)"]

    FTData --> AddHead["<b>Add Task Head</b><br/>Classification layer for labels<br/>Initialize from θ_pretrain"]

    AddHead --> FineTune["<b>Fine-tuning Phase</b><br/>Supervised Learning<br/>• Low learning rate (2e-5)<br/>• Few epochs (2-5)<br/>• Update all weights"]

    FineTune --> FTModel["<b>Fine-tuned Model</b><br/>θ_task<br/>Specialized for target task<br/>Retains general knowledge"]

    FTModel --> Deploy["🚀 Deploy<br/>Production Use"]

    Deploy --> End([End])

